title: Solitaire Stud Promise Ring Semi Mount
description:
This solitaire engagement ring uses a semi-bezel setting, and it’s made just for oval-cut gemstones. It has a clean design, and there are carefully placed grooves along the band—these grooves add more character to the ring and make the small details stand out. This ring is easy to wear every day, and it goes well with both plain bands and ones with diamonds on them. That makes it perfect for people who like subtle elegance.
Its clean, geometric look also catches the eye of people of all ages who love personalized styles. The semi-bezel setting works really well with different precious stones—whether it’s a diamond, emerald, sapphire, ruby, or amethyst, each stone gets to show off its shine.
You can pick from 10K, 14K, or 18K solid gold, and there are white, yellow, or rose gold options. We also take custom orders too—we can make the setting in platinum, and we’ll fit it to your specific gemstone size and finger measurement.
